data.description: Stunning and immaculate, this contemporary gem offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and convenient living. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this spacious haven spans over 2400 square feet, providing ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. Built in 2022, this home boasts the allure of a brand-new property, sparing you the anticipation of waiting for construction completion.Nestled in a vibrant and flourishing neighborhood, the property showcases fully landscaped grounds, creating an inviting outdoor oasis from the moment you arrive. This residence is perfectly situated in a rapidly growing area, offering the ideal combination of serenity and accessibility to amenities.Don't miss the chance to own this remarkable home that combines the allure of new construction with the convenience of move-in ready. Experience the joy of contemporary living, surrounded by picturesque landscaping and the promise of a bright future in an emerging community.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
